		<td><b>NES development manual?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does anyone have an official Nintendo Entertainment System development manual that they'd be willing to share to the NESdev community? 
<br />
<br />I talked to someone at #nesdev who has a copy, but he wasn't willing to share. He said most of the information in it was already available at nesdev.com and that it was written in terrible broken English. I offered to pay him for it, or to pay for shipping to borrow it, in order to scan it into PDF form, but he wasn't interested. 
<br />
<br />I thought it would be a great boon to have the original manual that American developers used to make games in the 80s.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


